CustomField.formula: IF(ISBLANK(animalos__Date_Returned__c), TODAY() - animalos__Date_Collected__c, IF(OR(animalos__Date_Returned__c = animalos__Date_Collected__c, animalos__Date_Collected__c = TODAY()), 1, animalos__Date_Returned__c - animalos__Date_Collected__c ))
CustomField.label: Total Time (Days)
